Read: 1. An overview of the 7th meeting of the High-Level Committee of Secretaries held on 16 October 2018.

November, 2018.
The Proposal: -
A long-term strategy for the education of persons with disabilities in the state has been formulated.
Regarding the constitution of the Committee to be constituted under the aforesaid reference No. The directions given under 1.
Accordingly, the matter of forming the committee was under the consideration of the government.
The Government's Decisions:
Hon'ble High-Level Committee of Secretaries dated 16th October, 2018 7th of 2018
Following the directions given in the meeting, the committee is being constituted as follows to formulate a long-term strategy for education of Divyangs in the state.

2. The committee will include in the general school in a phased manner the students belonging to the blind, mute, mentally retarded and orthopedic categories studying in the special schools run for the disabled in the state.
Set a long-term strategy for doing so.
